    "events_digest": "events_content_sha256 is defined over a canonical multiset of events (sorted by event_id). Reordering required events that share the same canonical projection therefore leaves events_content_sha256_match true.",
    "inconsistent_evaluation_result": "When the primary evaluation_result is pass but evaluation_internal_consistent is false (conflicting evaluation signals), the gate returns BLOCKED as fail-closed ambiguity rather than INVALID.",
